videos.headline: Jackson puts Duke on the board with 31-yd TD run
videos.description: Deon Jackson finds an opening and weaves through the Baylor defense for a 31-yard Duke touchdown.

videos.headline: Harris connects with Rahming for Duke TD
videos.description: Quentin Harris finds T.J. Rahming for a 28-yard touchdown pass to increase Duke's lead over Baylor.

videos.headline: Lloyd and Harris connect for 66-yd Duke TD
videos.description: Quentin Harris throws to Jonathan Lloyd for a 66-yard Duke touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Rahming hauls in second TD catch of game
videos.description: Quentin Harris connects with T.J. Rahming in the end zone for a 7-yard Duke touchdown.
